# 🧪 Postman Guide

---

## 📌 What is Postman?

Postman is a tool used to test APIs without a frontend.

---

## 🚀 Base URLs

Express:
http://localhost:3000

FastAPI:
http://localhost:8000

---

## 🔹 Test Cases

### ✅ Get All Students

- Method: GET  
- Endpoint: /api/students  

---

### ➕ Create Student

- Method: POST  
- Endpoint: /api/students  

Body:
```json
{
  "name": "Rahul",
  "email": "rahul@gmail.com",
  "course": "BCA",
  "age": 20
}
✏️ Update Student (PUT)
Method: PUT
Endpoint: /api/students/1
🔄 Partial Update (PATCH)
Method: PATCH
Endpoint: /api/students/1

Body:

{
  "age": 22
}
❌ Delete Student
Method: DELETE
Endpoint: /api/students/1
